research

my research interests fall in the area formal methods for desciption and
analysis of concurrent and distributed systems.  specific area i work in
include process algebra ... temporal logic ... analysis algorithms for
finite-state systems ... automatic verification tools ... semantic models of
system behavior ... operational semantics.






